reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Don’t cheap out !!! I bought a cheaper 50 cal antenna off Amazon previous to this one . Traveling from San Diego to Yuma Az( river), it got hammered with bugs, extremely hot weather , U.v.,Rays. It discolored fast from a matte black to silver/ gold .This product to this point has held up really well and not discolored at all . Install was extremely easy and to this point mechanical sound ..This antenna is worth the extra $$$ , and would have been cheaper in the long run!!

High quality product. Fits perfect. Instructions easy to follow. Well made and tough. Makes your whip look great. No issues with radio reception either and I live in the country, far away from radio towers. I would recommend this product to any of my friends.
